  "description": "A dramatic, silhouetted view of a bridge against a vibrant, fiery sunset. The sky is ablaze with horizontal bands of deep red, transitioning to orange near the horizon. The bridge appears as a dark, skeletal outline, its cables and supports sharply defined against the bright sky. A small, almost hidden green dot appears near the horizon. Dark foliage is visible in the foreground, partially obscuring the view, adding depth and a sense of framing. The water below reflects some of the sky's colors, creating a shimmering effect.",
